images.desc: This is what the intersection looks like when facing northward.

instructions: Go to the second floor of Williamson Hall. Make your way towards the south-most point of the building.
Enter the tunnel entrance, taking the first left (the right goes outside).
This will bring you to the first picture, you will be coming from the leftmost path, so you will navigate around the wall in front of you and take the pictured leftmost path.
At the end of that path is the entrance to Nolte Center level B.
